  "title": "遗忘",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"tjpQZB7d\"><b>遗忘</b>是知识逐渐从记忆中消失的过程。遗忘的主要原因是<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Interference\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">干扰</a><sup data-text=\"干扰\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/269974053\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>。对于简单神经网络中的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Complexity\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">原子知识</a><sup data-text=\"记忆复杂性\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/304800091\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>而言，干扰将导致<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Forgetting_curve\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">指数型遗忘</a><sup data-text=\"遗忘曲线\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/274352214\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>。这已被 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a> 所收集到的数据所证实。</p><p data-pid=\"wRgBATye\">欲了解更多，请参阅：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"97m9SdDQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Forgetting_curve\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">遗忘曲线</a><sup data-text=\"遗忘曲线\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/274352214\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"r40Lf5PU\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Mechanism_of_forgetting\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">遗忘机制</a><sup data-text=\"遗忘机制\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/265081034\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"fZyOIWoq\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Neurostatistical_model_of_memory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">记忆的神经统计学模型</a><sup data-text=\"记忆的神经统计模型\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/277483881\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"5\">[5]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"A0lylSYB\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Exponential_forgetting_via_interference_in_a_Hopfield_network\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Hopfield 网络中的干扰导致的指数型遗忘</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"HUZvro9Y\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Error_of_Ebbinghaus_forgetting_curve\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">艾宾浩斯遗忘曲线的错误</a><sup data-text=\"艾宾浩斯遗忘曲线的错误\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/156672476\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"6\">[6]</sup><br/> </li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ef5d178367356356603a071682a45926_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"346\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ef5d178367356356603a071682a45926_r.jpg\" data-original-token=\"v2-ef5d178367356356603a071682a45926\"/><figcaption>Exponential forgetting curve collected with SuperMemo 17</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"_ZScxAob\">图：经过相当于 6 次<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Optimum_interval\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">最佳间隔</a>复习后的，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a><sup data-text=\"什么是SuperMemo\" data-url=\"https://www.yuque.com/supermemo/wiki/supermemo\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"7\">[7]</sup> 学习材料的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Forgetting_curve\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">指数型遗忘曲线</a><sup data-text=\"遗忘曲线\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/274352214\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>。绘制的图表包含 14,550 次复习。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"dujCcay2\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Forgetting\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Forgetting - supermemo.guru</a><br/>本<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Glossary\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">词汇表</a>条目用于解释 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo_Guru\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo Guru</a> 系列中关于记忆、学习、创造力和问题解决的文本。</blockquote>",
